Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,真鉴陷入大危机了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不是她
